name: Yelena and pink Cosmos
description:
Yelena was revived in a strange place from where she had previously existed. People are dressed weirdly here, and there is no internet. Yelena thought that she was probably dreaming. Yes, she must be dreaming.

Yelena meets Florre by accident when starving and staring at sweets in a bakery. As a result, there have been a lot of crazy stories to follow.

Yelena is a beautiful, strong , self-assured woman who is full of energy. If anyone makes she angry. She was ready to punch him with her fighting skills.

Her flower is pink Cosmos. The meanings of Cosmos include beauty, balance, modesty, joy.
